  <brief_title>Post-PCI:Cardiac Imaging in Patients With Diabetes to Detect Coronary Artery Blockages Previously Opened by Angioplasty</brief_title>
  <official_title>Cardiolite-406; A Phase IV Open-Label, Randomized, Multi-Center Trial To Evaluate The Ability of Cardiolite Stress MPI to Detect Asymptomatic Restenosis in Diabetic Patients Who Have Undergone Percutaneous Coronary Intervention</official_title>
  <sponsors>
