  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this clinical research study is determine if patients with diabetes that have
      undergone previous opening of a heart blockage may have a blockage that is not causing any
      symptoms that may be detected by imaging with Cardiolite.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
